Package com.aldodaquino.cobra.gui

Class Status

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aldodaquino.cobra.gui.Status
  • public class Status
extends java.lang.Object
    The Status class. A Status object is generated in the StarterPanel. Contains all the information about the user and the catalog and is passed through the classes.
    Version:
    1.0.
    Author:
    Aldo D'Aquino.
